description:
&lt;p&gt;We are currently looking for an experienced social worker who is a suitably motivated and skilled practitioner seeking to work within the arena of adult social care across Paignton and Brixham.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a permanent post located within a multi disciplinary community team providing high quality social care services across the bay to a range of adults from 18 years and onwards. The ideal post holder will have a range of skills and knowledge that will meet the demands and complexities of the service users within our locality. This will provide the ideal opportunity for a practitioner who embraces challenge.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Additionally we are looking for a dynamic and inspirational practitioner who is able to safeguard vulnerable adults whilst working with choice, risk and person centered outcomes, capacity and service user self-determination. This is a busy sea side social care team who works with a varied case load that promotes opportunities for development learning and progression.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is open to qualified Social Workers with the right attributes to enhance this team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are looking for a new challenge, enjoy variety in your work and wish to be part of a team striving to make a difference for our community by supporting people to live independently in their own home, then we want to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
